
# VALID COMMUNITY REQUESTS

### route
GET http://localhost:4000 HTTP/1.1

### List all user-groups
GET http://localhost:4000/api/user-groups HTTP/1.1


### List all user-groups filtered by genre
GET http://localhost:4000/api/user-groups?genre=action&isRead=false HTTP/1.1

### List all user-groups filtered by isRead-status
GET http://localhost:4000/api/user-groups?isRead=false HTTP/1.1


### Get a certain community by id
GET http://localhost:4000/api/user-groups/6116464fb6e88b50a221c2f6 HTTP/1.1

### Create a new community
POST http://localhost:4000/api/user-groups HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {
    "name": "Klasse 3a",
    "type": "class community"
  },
  {
    "name": "Klasse 4a",
    "type": "class community"
  },
  {
    "name": "Klasse 5a",
    "type": "class community"
  }
]


### PATCH community by id (with existing id) (ie. update)
PATCH http://localhost:4000/api/user-groups/6103d1ca783a5b23d7016f68 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isRead": true
}

### DELETE a community by id
DELETE  http://localhost:4000/api/user-groups/6103da28ffe84d2c7cc1172f HTTP/1.1



